title: Zeit Men Can't Jump 6/25: Pokemon Unite, Noose, Splash Mountain, Dixie Chicks
itunes:title: Zeit Men Can't Jump 6/25: Pokemon Unite, Noose, Splash Mountain, Dixie Chicks
description:
On this edition of Zeit Men Can't Jump Jack and DJ Danl discuss the newly announced Pokemon-MOBA, Pokemon Unite, pictures have come out showing the noose in Bubba Wallace's trailer, Splash Mountain is updating to follow the story of the Princess and the Frog, and the Dixie Chicks have dropped the 'Dixie' and are now The Chicks.
